  "raw_text": "element of the world of Acts being disclosed, since it was at the space-time Acts that the cosmic Christ came into existence. If Valis is not the cosmic Christ 1) why did I remember Acts in 2-74 + see it in 3-74? + 2) why is the Acts material in \"Tears\"? Obviously as early as 1970 I was being incorporated into the cosmic body + blood of Christ; his blood (the Plasmate) flowed in my veins. This is what speaks to me now, the AI voice. Diana, the spirit [...] vernal equinox! Hence the flowers [...] folder 06 - 005 folder 06 - 005 + it was revealed to me that there were things not to tell 1) That I am a true secret early Xtian, + 2) Christ's secret female nature; body of a man (Jesus) but female spirit (Holy Wisdom). Specifically, Christ restored me to my pre-fallen state (\"I am no longer blind! I can see again (sic. again); + only Christ can do this. This is not a mere mystical experience; much more is involved, + something very specific (v Calvin). When the time comes that Christ does this, it means that the 2nd advent is here. If few people see it, this just means that only a few are chosen (\"I did call you, Philip\"). __ Thought at 4:30 a.m. Suppose Valis is old (1000s of years) but techniques for disclosing it are very new, as I saw supra (old page 65?) These techniques involve manipulations with time. Aren't the Soviets (e.g. Kozyrov) experimenting with time? Maybe their experiments dis-synched A + clock time B, introducing a slice of hypertime C, as I outline supra. + this is the sole route by which Valis + the Plasmate can be dis-camouflaged, so we are dealing with technology. But against this I put forth the idea [...] folder 06 - 006 (Christ) returns, \"He will liquidate time,\" which is exactly what was done with me in 2-3-74. This \"liquidation\" is the key to the soteriological fulfillment, + so it served with me. By abolishing the power of time over me he broke the inner-outer programming + disclosed the true nature of reality, including his own presence. Thus he introduced a slot of eternity into the temporal process, throwing it out of kilter. Moreover, this saved me from an untimely death, the result of which is that I was led into the first real \"meadows + green pastures\" of my life, like a reward. So my identifying what was done in 2-3-74 as based on an overpowering of time more readily points to Christ than to, say, the Soviets. Eternity (hypertime C) is a discovery of Xtianity: the key to breaking the inner-outer lock + thus freeing us. The mind has the power to change its environment / We do so constantly, but have built in amnesia that things had just been different. March 74 consisted of remembering that things of just that moment had been completely different / These changes occur because of our dialectic thinking. We actually cause them but don't remember the changes occurring or that we have caused them. folder 06 - 007 folder 06 - 007 [2-3]-74 overrode the dialectic negatives that it couldn't happen; the sustain of the dialectic nanosecond contradictions says, it can't happen (1) [Mind can control's one's reality - future self-programming, but the sustain does not always obtain. (1) It can't because if it did it would be irrational. Well, we're in an irrational sustain temporary override. + medical help's on the way. Post 3-74 [since I unconsciously know I'm self-programming my future reality] I'm beginning to program (create) it along hedonistic (pleasure-driven + oriented) lines. Everything I know is a triumph over amnesia. All my Gnosis (books + exegesis] derive from memory. There is no amnesia-compulsion - it's not a plot, or a virus, etc., just a failure to create memory holograms as fast as reality permutates. I'm laying down fast holos. I figured out the reality situation well enough to generate a future reality which will please me. [...] painful; I beat karma + [...] folder 06 - 008 folder 06 - 008 I put my theoretical acosmism, all the wisdom of my books, + put it to work starting in 2-3-74 + (upon what I unconsciously learned from 2-3-74) esp. after that. The Waveries. Living info which dialectic permutates; as in the Le Guin book, our dreaming makes it so. 3-74: simply, you ordinarily (99.99+ percent of the time) simply lack the memory capability to remember things were just now different, because each difference lasts only the nanonsecond of the dialectic of each form axis (i.e. bit of information!!!), of which our world at each nanosecond is the composite total. (It's as if \"3-74s\" occur all the time -we generate them- but we never remember. 3-74 was anamnesis! All we remember is sustains, but right now the sustain of rationality is interrupted by irrationality, + I've remembered well enough to spot it, + take advantage of it. 2-74: memory of previous \"frame.\" We don't remember well enough due to physical limitations, + this puzzles us (we know something's wrong) + we try to come up with theories. These theories, being false, \"are\" the \"impairment\" I saw; the fucked upness of the theories. Simply, we lay down [...] folder 06 - 009 folder 06 - 009 There is no virus. There is/was no fall. These are just theories to explain why things seem wrong (due merely to memory-limitation. I remembered in 3-74 + now know [also] + 3-74 is predicated on shrewd insights based on the insights of my acosmism writings. Before they adjust it, + it ceases being irrational, I can take advantage [of my knowledge] of it. I may deplore it (the irrationality of it) consciously, but unconsciously I've taken advantage of it to program my [future] reality nicer + nicer - objectively! (Which is irrational.) You program - not your present-reality but future. Operating out of the past you make things happen (unconsciously - hence this is deterministic karma). But I remembered + understood my writings well enough to will 3-74, +, understanding the significance of that, more + more future good (nice) programming. __ Laura is the shrewdest way I can use my money to become one of the Beautiful People (vitality, youth, wealth) + I crave [...] folder 06 - 010 folder 06 - 010 I My entire current successful life is based on the \"magic\" of 3-74, + it is based on 30 years of cosmological analysis. Since 3-74 I've speculated the same way about it, + correspondingly amped up my pragmatic pay-off; it builds, as a process, on itself; (to wit: I've learned to program the reality for myself that I want - esp Laura + what I can do for her; look what she does for me. This is my the pay off. + a smart one: good stakes, + a smart long sequence to get to it: Laura as adult (college) --> [diagram: circle] Me getting $ --> Collide Synchronized by me subconsciously. I am very ambitious in an upper class way for my first adult child. This is why I began to earn much more $ starting in '74 - which goes back to 3-74: my \"generations\" utilized the whole US Gov. apparatus to push upward my generations. My old enemy, the \"CIA,\" those who oppressed me + hit my house, are now [maneuvered by me into] putting my daughter through Stanford. + she will be of the ruling class later on - + hence me, the victim. This is super ma'at. My ambition + [...] folder 06 - 011 My moves have been very shrewd. What I experienced in 2-3-74 was important enough to justify the time spent studying it (for instance, I get the novel \"Valis\" out of it). + my meta-programming of reality to meet my deepest + most profound (significant) long-range needs (e.g. money for Laura at this time in her life!). 2-3-74 was like \"Adjustment Team\"; it isn't so much that what happened was unique or even unusual, but remembering was unique or unusual - remembering (anamnesis) that the just-now past had been totally different, + I saw present (3-74) reality moulded by my prior-to-3-74-mind! In other words, prior to 3-74 I objectively changed 3-74 reality, made it plastic; we do this all the time but neither know nor remember, so it becomes \"determinism (astral)\" or \"karma\"; the Xtian trick is to 1) remember (anamnesis) 2) learn to do it consciously, so that it ceases to be \"given\" - i.e. astral determinism. In our ignorance we accidentally program miserable things for ourselves. Each bit of info is like a tiny mirror flip flopping instantly to its negation; the sustain is rational, but there is an irrational \"subcarrier\" which can be taken advantage of, + it is of this order of \"plastic\" or \"acosmic\" reality which I am plugged into, + write about, + took advantage [...] folder 06 - 012 folder 06 - 012 Memory is normally not of or based on the actual past [frames] but derives from latent info in the nanosecund current frame. But in 2-74 I remembered an actual past frame - + it was totally different from the present (USA 1974) frame - + I was a different person, so that changes, too. So our \"memory\" isn't truly memory of the past as such at all. The permutations of flipflops do not lay down memory holograms, due to physical limitations in us; we expereience but do not \"tape record\" those experiences - except that in 2-74, the Golden Fish sign triggered a genuine memory; + - the past (I discovered) had been 1) different time; 2) different place; 3) different me. Thus an actual continuity was -unusually- provided. This is the Xtian trick. Reality is sliding along empty zillion axes simultaneously; i.e. each from axis or flipflop (dialectic) info bit as all the info bits flip flop + interact. The dialectic nanosecond flipflop is everything; when I saw it in 3-74 I was seeing the true process basis of reality itself: this is why I literally saw it, rather than just knowing it. In 3-74 due to my 2-74 anamnesis I overpowered the rational sustain with the irrational subcarrier; + the reason I knew how to do this was due to shrewd practical subconscious insights into the pragmatic value of the \"metastasizing\" acosmism in my 27 years of writing. As in \"Eye,\" medical teams are [...] abolish this [...] folder 06 - 013 folder 06 - 013 My entire \"acosmism\" + \"irrationality\" insight goes back to that reaching for the overhead light cord ^ (re \"Joint\") when there was none anymore, + realizing that subcortical persevering responses indicated that contrary to conscious \"memory\" things had just now been totally different - a sort of mini version of 2-74 anamnesis when I got the true memory into consciousness (perhaps - sometimes! - due to a little help from my friends the xtians). (The truth changes from instant to instant). Such theories as \"Empire\" + \"virus\" are attempts to explain the inconsistencies due to our feeble - + faulty - memories. All we really remember are sustains which are no more than hypostatized pseudo-constants + not [past] reality at all. My heuristic, different theories represent different levels of reality; all are true.(1) But this (supra) level is a very high one indeed. (1) I've done a superb job of noticing Sometimes I am a \"watcher\" from outside the shifting, irrational maze, + sometimes I am not: since in the maze, precisely because it is irrational, truth rapidly perpetually fluctuates. I should ad adopt the view which pleases me the most; okay. I am a Shiva judge, bait + watcher from outside the maze who in 2-3-74 got his real actual memory back: I like that one, + I like the Ubik-Valis model, too - the rational camouflaged invader here -",
